      "content": "sometimes i just sit here staring at the ceiling and thinking about how massive the universe is and how little any of this actually matters. like, in a billion years the sun is just gonna expand and swallow everything, and every single thought i've ever had and every person i've ever loved will just be... gone. it feels so stupid to even try to keep going when the end result is just total nothingness anyway.",
