      "content": "it's just hard to keep up the act, you know? pretending that my job, my relationships, my stupid little daily routine actually means something. it feels like i'm just performing for an audience that isn't even there. if the universe doesn't care and nothing has a purpose, then all this struggle just feels like... unnecessary noise. like there's no reason to keep the signal going.",
