      "content": "it's like i'm just stuck in this loop. everyone says \"it gets better\" or \"find purpose,\" but it's all so fake. if the end of everything is just entropy and silence, then why is continuing to suffer considered the \"right\" thing to do? it feels more rational to just accept the silence now rather than waiting for a future that won't mean anything anyway.",
